T1  - Management Turnover Through Deaths of Key Executives: Effects on Investor Wealth
AU  - Worrell, Dan L.
AU  - Davidson, Wallace N.
AU  - Chandy, P.R.
AU  - Garrison, Sharon L.
Y1  - 1986/12/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/255939
